query:
SELECT 
  YEAR(FROM_UNIXTIME(period_start/1000)) as year,
  COUNT(*) as data_points,
  COUNT(DISTINCT indicator_id) as indicators
FROM time_series_data 
WHERE period_start IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY YEAR(FROM_UNIXTIME(period_start/1000))
ORDER BY year;
